<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> بابُ قَوْلِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«لَا تَسْأَلُوا أَهْلَ الْكِتَابِ عَنْ شَيْءٍ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
